BT /F2 15.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 650.00 Tm (Abstract) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 620.00 Tm (CytoCV is a web-based analysis system for DeltaVision microscopy of mitotic yeast cells. The) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 606.00 Tm (platform integrates authenticated web workflows, DeltaVision-specific metadata parsing, Mask) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 592.00 Tm (R-CNN-based segmentation, plugin-scoped per-cell quantification, and retention-aware result) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 578.00 Tm (management in a single Django application. The current codebase supports four logical) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 564.00 Tm (channel roles \(DIC, DAPI, mCherry, and GFP\), but only DIC is universally required.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 550.00 Tm (Additional fluorescence requirements are derived from the selected analysis plugins and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 536.00 Tm (optional upload-time validation policy.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 500.00 Tm (System Objective) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 470.00 Tm (The system is designed to reduce manual analysis effort while preserving the relationship) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 456.00 Tm (between source microscopy stacks, derived segmentation artifacts, and exported measurements.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 442.00 Tm (CytoCV therefore treats run configuration, channel mapping, scale context, and plugin) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 428.00 Tm (selection as first-class workflow state rather than transient UI detail.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 392.00 Tm (Input Model) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 362.00 Tm (CytoCV ingests DeltaVision \(.dv\) files that can be interpreted as channel stacks. The) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 348.00 Tm (implementation recognizes four logical channel roles:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 326.00 Tm (- ) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 70.00 326.00 Tm (DIC, used for structural segmentation and CNN preprocessing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 308.00 Tm (- ) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 70.00 308.00 Tm (DAPI, used for legacy nucleus-related measurements) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 290.00 Tm (- ) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 70.00 290.00 Tm (mCherry, used for red-signal contour and intensity measurements) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 272.00 Tm (- ) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 70.00 272.00 Tm (GFP, used for green-signal contour, intensity, and dot-classification measurements) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 252.00 Tm (The software does not require all four roles in every run. The minimum baseline requirement) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 238.00 Tm (is DIC. The default modern configuration requires DIC, mCherry, and GFP. DAPI becomes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 224.00 Tm (required only when a legacy DAPI-centered plugin is selected or when full-wavelength) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 210.00 Tm (validation is enabled.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 174.00 Tm (Validation Logic) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 144.00 Tm (Upload-time validation is controlled by the effective requirement set assembled in) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 130.00 Tm (core.views.experiment and core.metadata_processing.error_handling.dv_validation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 106.00 Tm (The effective required channels are formed as:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 84.00 Tm (1. ) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.50 Tf 1 0 0 1 70.00 84.00 Tm (the baseline segmentation requirement DIC) Tj ET
